summary: As a researcher I'm focussed on cell - / molecular biology and biochemistry. Currently I'm doing my PhD on the development of thermostable nanodiscs for drug development at Leiden University in the laboratory of Marcellus Ubbink. We investigate protein-lipid nanoparticles with pharmaceutical applications.
